events.info: Discover the hero inside us all when Disney On Ice returns with the magical adventures of favorite Disney stars brought to life like never before. Step inside the music and magic of Encanto with Mirabel and her family as they learn that everyone has a special gift. Sail away with Moana and Maui on their brave journey across the ocean to return the heart of Te Fiti. Join Anna and Elsa on their quest to protect their kingdom. Be inspired by the Disney Princesses with stories of courage, determination and kindness as you swim under the sea with Ariel, explore an enchanted castle with Belle, and belt out your dreams with Rapunzel. Hosted by Mickey and Minnie, experience world-class ice skating, iconic music, and stunning costumes that will make Disney On Ice presents Find Your Hero an experience the whole family will treasure forever. *Note: Costumes not permitted for guests 14 years & older. Visit DisneyOnIce.com for more information.
events.pleaseNote: All guests age 2 & older are required to have a ticket. - No costumes for guests 14 & older. - Character Experiences Available. Access to a private event with interactive time and photo opportunities. Each guest, ages 2 and up, must have both a Character Experience ticket and a Disney On Ice show ticket to attend the Character Experience. Children must be accompanied by an adult. - Please monitor the venue website for venue policies, including health and safety protocols, which are subject to change. - All tickets are subject to availability. - Prices are subject to change. - Visit DisneyOnIce.com for more info.

ageRestrictions.ageRuleDescription: All guests age 2 and older are required to have a ticket.

venues.name: Bojangles Coliseum

boxOfficeInfo.phoneNumberDetail: Phone: 704.335.3100 (Tickets cannot be ordered over the phone. Call 800.745.3000 to purchase tickets)
boxOfficeInfo.openHoursDetail: The main box office is located on the south side of Bojangles Coliseum. Regular hours are Friday 10am to 5pm. Show days we open 2 hours prior to the event start time at Bojangles Coliseum Box Office.
boxOfficeInfo.acceptedPaymentDetail: Cash, Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Discover. All credit card purchases require a photo ID.
boxOfficeInfo.willCallDetail: Will call orders can be picked up at the box office during normal business hours or right before the event. (Note: Certain events may not allow will call pick-up until the day of the performance.) Please bring a picture id, the credit card used to make the purchase and the order number. Tickets will only be released to the person whose name is on the account.

venues.parkingDetail: Facility parking lots are located immediately to the left after turning onto Briar Creek. Auxiliary parking lots (if needed) are located immediately to the right. ADA parking is available. For most events, parking is included in your ticket price. There are some events that is not included in your ticket. Parking fees range from $6.00 - $10.00 per vehicle.
venues.accessibleSeatingDetail: Accessible seating is available for patrons with disabilities. Tickets can be purchased through all sales channels. Those wishing to purchase accessible seats are allowed to have up to three companions sitting with them (based on availability). Bojangles Coliseum strongly encourages those needing to purchase tickets in accessible seating areas to do so as far in advance as possible. All accessible seating will be allocated on a first-come, first-served basis. Every effort will be made on the day of an event to accommodate those needing accessible seats but are holding a ticket for a conventional seat but all such exchanges are based on availability. Accessible seats are located in Sections 106, 108, 110, 121, 123 and 125.

generalInfo.generalRule: Video cameras, flash cameras, laser pointers, outside food or beverage, large bags/backpacks and weapons are prohibited at Bojangles Coliseum. All patrons are subject to search. No re-entry. Bojangles Coliseum is a tobacco-free facility. No tobacco products or e-cigarettes may be used on the premises, either inside or outside. Prices listed include all applicable taxes.
generalInfo.childRule: Children 2 and under do not need a ticket for entry provided they sit on adults lap. Certain events may have different rules regarding the age which children need a ticket.

venues.accessibleSeatingDetail: Accessible seating is available for patrons with disabilities. Tickets can be purchased through all sales channels. Those wishing to purchase accessible seats are allowed to have up to three companions sitting with them (based on availability). Bojangles Coliseum strongly encourages those needing to purchase tickets in accessible seating areas to do so as far in advance as possible. All accessible seating will be allocated on a first-come, first-served basis. Every effort will be made on the day of an event to accommodate those needing accessible seats but are holding a ticket for a conventional seat but all such exchanges are based on availability. Accessible seats are located in Sections 106, 108, 110, 121, 123 and 125.

generalInfo.childRule: Children 2 and under do not need a ticket for entry provided they sit on adults lap. Certain events may have different rules regarding the age which children need a ticket.

events.info: Discover the hero inside us all when Disney On Ice returns with the magical adventures of favorite Disney stars brought to life like never before. Step inside the music and magic of Encanto with Mirabel and her family as they learn that everyone has a special gift. Sail away with Moana and Maui on their brave journey across the ocean to return the heart of Te Fiti. Join Anna and Elsa on their quest to protect their kingdom. Be inspired by the Disney Princesses with stories of courage, determination and kindness as you swim under the sea with Ariel, explore an enchanted castle with Belle, and belt out your dreams with Rapunzel. Hosted by Mickey and Minnie, experience world-class ice skating, iconic music, and stunning costumes that will make Disney On Ice presents Find Your Hero an experience the whole family will treasure forever. *Note: Costumes not permitted for guests 14 years & older. Visit DisneyOnIce.com for more information.
